        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>What are your daily habits? What time do you get up, etc.?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 30 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I get up with my children at zeven o'clock. I have a shower. I get dressed and I always have breakfast. I go to work in my bookshop from eight o'clock until zeven o'clock. In the evening, I do the children's homework, I cook.  I sometimes watch Tv and go to bed at eleven o'clock.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </body>
